      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0419P1_20040331_WH_35'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-wright' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0419P1_20040331_WH_35' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Wright' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-wright" title="Mr David Wright">David Wright</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            My hon. Friend is right. We need a comprehensive energy strategy, particularly for industry. Coke prices are important to the energy sector.
